HEADWORD: alexiterical
<hw>a*lex`i*ter"ic*al</hw>
<pr>(⟦adot⟧*l⟦ecr⟧ks`⟦icr⟧*t⟦ecr⟧r"⟦icr⟧*k⟦ait⟧l)</pr>, }</mhw>
<pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <grk>'alexhth`rios</grk> fit to keep off or
help, fr. <grk>'alexhth`r</grk> one who keeps off, helper;
